title: EPISODE 299: Elon Conquers Twitter, will the POWs be released? w/ Libby Emmons
description:
In today’s episode of Human Events Daily, Jack Posobiec is joined by the Editor-In-Chief at Post Millennial, Libby Emmons! The two not only discuss the guilty verdict for Waukesha Parade murderer Darrell Brooks, but also the judge ordered investigation into a reddit group for concerning claims about interference with a juror. Elon Musk is progressing with the Twitter takeover, and is experiencing a leftist employee exodus from the company - what does this mean for the future of twitter, and the POWs from the former leftist regime? Finally, House Progressives, the supposed anti-war wing, came out with a diplomatic plan for peace, and quickly retracted said diplomatic plan. Why? Poso and Libby dive deep into analysis on this shameful walkback.  


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
